                                     <ol> <li> Vinzu and others sa,id :-
                                     1. 0 great lord, the lord of the gods and the prescriber of worldly conventions, we know you to be Siva and
                                     Brahman, thanks to your favour. 
                                     Rudrasamhitii 461
                                     2. 0 lord Siva, why do you delude us by your illusion
                                     which is inscrutable and which deludes people always.
                                     3. You are the supreme Brahman, greater than Prak:rti
